. We provide critical M_star/d2 values for suppression of H2-cooling, with\nanalytic fits, which can be used in future studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2016 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2017 23:01:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
