02 CBs in the Large Magellanic Cloud are used to determine a distance\nmodulus to the galaxy of $(m-M_V)_0^{\\rm LMC}=18.41\\pm0.20$ mag.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2016 04:30:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-07"}
