 scatter in [$\\alpha$/Fe] may\nreflect stochasticity in the chemical evolution of low-mass galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2016 05:53:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-05"}
